def minimum_move_to_fit_table(W, H, x1, y1, x2, y2, w, h):
    (x1, x2) = (min(x1, x2), max(x1, x2))
    (y1, y2) = (min(y1, y2), max(y1, y2))
    min_move = float('inf')
    if w < W - (x2 - x1):
        rx = max(x1, W - x2)
        mx = max(0, w - rx)
        min_move = min(min_move, mx)
    if h <= H - (y2 - y1):
        ry = max(y1, H - y2)
        my = max(0, h - ry)
        min_move = min(min_move, my)
    if min_move == float('inf'):
        return -1
    return min_move
